								<wikidot:authorUserId>3146689</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Thanks a lot for your praise. :P</p> <p>Well, I can say that this work was inspired by previous tales as well. I just decided to move a bit away from social commentary and towards how scary it is to lose your identity. Because IMO what Keelee is doing to people is very creepy, and I thought it might work in a tale.</p> 
				 	]]>
